category: Lua Database
requires: lua postgres
external-source: lua-sql
sdesc: "Lua database connectivity package (PostgreSQL driver)"
ldesc: "LuaSQL is a simple interface from Lua to a DBMS. It enables a 
Lua program to:
* Connect to ODBC, MySQL, SQLite and PostgreSQL databases;
* Execute arbitrary SQL statements;
* Retrieve results in a row-by-row cursor fashion."
